&lt;p&gt;You’ll join the mobile engineering effort within our Product, eXperiences &amp;amp; Engineering org, working side by side with the engineering lead who owns mobile and the product manager shaping where the apps go next. The setup is small and largely greenfield, so your footprint is big from day one: you help define how mobile works at Make, not just maintain what exists, and your features reach users on iOS and Android worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Rapidly prototype, implement features, and optimize mobile experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Interface with backend engineering teams to align on API contracts and data integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Submit pull requests, receive structured feedback, and pair program on complex problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Use AI tools like Claude Code, Cursor, or Copilot as part of your daily workflow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Work on features used by thousands of global users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
