&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Fluent English (spoken and written)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Solid software engineering foundations: clean logic, problem-solving, and a good grasp of programming basics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Basic knowledge or experience in mobile development: Swift/SwiftUI, Kotlin, or cross-platform concepts (side projects, school projects, or hobby apps count)&lt;/li&gt;
