&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive&lt;/strong&gt; competitive intelligence for your domain — maintaining a current, credible view of how Make&#39;s capabilities compare.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analyze&lt;/strong&gt; launch performance through both qualitative and quantitative lenses, extracting and disseminating the insights that sharpen future release strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Represent&lt;/strong&gt; Make as a subject matter expert for your domain in webinars and external events — presenting with confidence and clarity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Champion&lt;/strong&gt; AI tools across your own workflow to accelerate output quality, reduce cycle time on launches, and model the same automation-first mindset Make enables for its customers.&lt;/li&gt;
