&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research, write, review, revise, and publish technical documentation for the Make Public Help Center and Developer Hub.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create clear and comprehensive API documentation to support users in integrating apps with our platform.&lt;/li&gt;
