&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make is the platform to manage all your automations and AI agents in one visual landscape – for teams driving business impact without relying on developers. Part of Celonis, a global leader in process intelligence recognized on the Forbes Cloud 100 for seven consecutive years, we&#39;re headquartered in Prague, Czechia, with hubs in Madrid, Munich, Raleigh, and Pristina, and teams across the UK, France, India, and the Netherlands, among other locations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4&gt;The Team&lt;/h4&gt;
